company_name: HANS BRUSTMANN GMBH & CO.KG FABRIK UND GROßHANDEL IN ZOOARTIKEL
information: The company HANS BRUSTMANN GMBH & CO.KG FABRIK UND GROßHANDEL IN ZOOARTIKEL, is a Distributor, founded in 1973, which operates in the Feeds for animal farming industry. It is based in Oestrich-Winkel, Germany.
